sections.heading: Attachment; several orders against same defendant; time of service
sections.text: When there are several orders of attachment against the same defendant, they shall be executed in the order in which they are received by the sheriff.SourceR.S.1867, Code ยง 204, p. 426;R.S.1913, ยง 7738;C.S.1922, ยง 8682;C.S.1929, ยง 20
